Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德….
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德….
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在霍夫曼遗迹那里见到埃洱了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的精神还不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他现在正在艾尔大陆上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最近得到的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们运气真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到那么大的海啸竟然都没有受什么伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过….
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德和雷恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船晃得还真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想不想出去走走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜….妳也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片森林…..感觉真诡异耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一路上，似乎都没有看到什么小动物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片森林完全感觉不到生气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不会又是因为…魔石索沙的影响吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…照妳这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林里的动物难道…全被魔物…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么味道啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是受到魔石索沙影响所冒出的毒气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一情况比我以前看到的还要糟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那些魔物的魂魄的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小长?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼!闻了我就想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看这一带…现在已经变成这些魔物的栖息地了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔物的栖息地?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾…..这片大地已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们现在还是尽快离开的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经没有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们搭船去拉克尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地方….至少比较安全一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的很感谢各位对我们的关心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早就已经决定要留在这片土地了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们从出生就是在这里长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片大地就像我们的母亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你们忍心拋下已经生病的母亲离开吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们活到这把年纪从来没离开过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都爱这片土地，也以这片土地为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们生长的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的要死的话，也要死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话啊…..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样太奇怪了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这样是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这并不表示我们放弃希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是放弃希望而一心等死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是我们还一直抱着一丝希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『当这块大地－艾克斯贝尔…\N受到欺凌，民不聊生的时候…』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『便会出现一位异国打扮的勇者』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『勇者高举着光剑，拯救苦难的人民』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的…勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥佩拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天慢慢凉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能借我看一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这似乎还可以使用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问……这是用来做什么的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得克劳德一路上都非常宝贝它的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪妳会不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了和远方的人说话而发明的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和远方的人说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多远呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和宇宙空间通话也许不太可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是在这个行星上的话…应该可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们能用它跟克劳德说话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕没有办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方必须也要有一个相同的机器才能够通话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳现在有什么打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔大陆太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在也只能折回拉克尔大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是妳想…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是雪萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪萤火虫?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这附近的人，都把它叫做『大地的精灵』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也认为它们是喜悦和希望的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜悦…..和希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像奥佩拉找寻埃洱奈斯特一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去找克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道艾尔大陆现在非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不想逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想离开这个地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何，我一定要见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也许比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啰，我们也要和蕾娜一起去找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…..我们是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧，小长?小圆?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道还不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还动得了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一定能再动的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊….每次看到你的时候，我都会想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是什么东西\N驱使你对每件事…抱持…这种信念?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想要超越一座山…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一座高耸的大山…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想要超越那座山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别看我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脑袋最不灵光了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受损太严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一般的科学家恐怕得投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你放心，我一定能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德他们有没有事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德他们在那波大海啸来袭之前就上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想他们应该不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他们在海上遇到了海啸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可就什么都完啰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个悲观主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳也用不着踢我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔利亚?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是魔石索沙坠落的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的情况怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔利亚…过去曾经被喻为艺术之都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是艾尔大陆上最繁荣的一个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……自从那颗魔石掉下来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的荣景都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且….现在那个地方已经成了魔物出没的魔域了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类根本就连一步都不敢随便靠近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些魔物都是由魔石索沙繁衍出来的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊!我们就在这里吃便当吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么话啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是才刚刚上路的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在发育饿得快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小长跟小圆呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快，快，快，你给我乖乖的走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子再饿一点吃起便当来，才会更好吃的，艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛…塞丽奴….
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们救救我啊….
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎么啦 蕾娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:13:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到克劳德的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经看不到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我到这边去找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那边找…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你发出的声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要….
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…..求求你……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:16:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你….救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见面以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他见面之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳还好吧?蕾娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德….
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧，现在由我来对付你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有用?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绝对不会让你伤害她的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是为了保护同伴才努力撑住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想….他一定会好好的守护妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此他才能保有自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火凤破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的…勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了….
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说古书解读出来了，是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚刚解开…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容到底是怎么说的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古书里到底写了些什么?奇斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…我在路上再告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最要紧的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得立刻通知克劳德他们这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:20:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个机械…..到底是什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来魔石还可以激活机械啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想它应该原本就是一种用来激活机械的能量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个情况现在好象越来越超出我们想象了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石…索沙…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做艾修顿．安卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有骗你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这一次真的有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克尔赫普修不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥佩拉又突然消失了踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连能源石也被人给抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场仗怎么打都不可能有胜算的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我们为什么到现在还没有丧失希望呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  StarOceanEX 『朋友』
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说勇者根本就不存在这是什么意思啊?
